{"article_id":"KCEBL9JYQgXAYX60","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"WASHINGTON -","depth":1},{"id":1,"text":"A white police officer in North Charleston , S.C. , was charged with murder on Tuesday","depth":6},{"id":2,"text":"after a video surfaced","depth":7},{"id":3,"text":"showing him shooting in the back and killing an apparently unarmed black man","depth":8},{"id":4,"text":"while the man ran away .","depth":8},{"id":5,"text":"The officer , Michael T. Slager , 33 , said","depth":7},{"id":6,"text":"he had feared for his life","depth":8},{"id":7,"text":"because the man had taken his stun gun in a scuffle after a traffic stop on Saturday .","depth":8},{"id":8,"text":"A video , however , shows the officer firing eight times","depth":7},{"id":9,"text":"as the man , Walter L. Scott , 50 , fled .","depth":7},{"id":10,"text":"The North Charleston mayor announced the state charges at a news conference Tuesday evening .","depth":4},{"id":11,"text":"The shooting came on the heels of high-profile instances of police officers ' using lethal force in New York , Cleveland , Ferguson , Mo. , and elsewhere .","depth":4},{"id":12,"text":"The deaths have set off a national debate","depth":6},{"id":13,"text":"over whether the police are too quick to use force , particularly in cases","depth":7},{"id":14,"text":"involving black men .","depth":7},{"id":15,"text":"A White House task force has recommended a host of changes to the nation ' s police policies ,","depth":6},{"id":16,"text":"and President Obama sent Attorney General Eric H. Holder Jr. to cities around the country","depth":7},{"id":17,"text":"to try to improve police relations with minority neighborhoods .","depth":7},{"id":18,"text":"North Charleston is South Carolina ' s third-largest city , with a population of about 100,000 .","depth":5},{"id":19,"text":"African-Americans make up about 47 percent of residents ,","depth":7},{"id":20,"text":"and whites account for about 37 percent .","depth":7},{"id":21,"text":"The Police Department is about 80 percent white ,","depth":7},{"id":22,"text":"according to data","depth":8},{"id":23,"text":"collected by the Justice Department in 2007 , the most recent period available .","depth":8},{"id":24,"text":"\" When you ' re wrong ,","depth":7},{"id":25,"text":"you ' re wrong , \"","depth":7},{"id":26,"text":"Mayor Keith Summey said during the news conference .","depth":6},{"id":27,"text":"\" And","depth":6},{"id":28,"text":"if you make a bad decision ,","depth":8},{"id":29,"text":"don ' t care if you ' re behind the shield or just a citizen on the street ,","depth":8},{"id":30,"text":"you have to live by that decision . \"","depth":7},{"id":31,"text":"The shooting unfolded","depth":7},{"id":32,"text":"after Officer Slager stopped the driver of a Mercedes-Benz with a broken taillight ,","depth":7},{"id":33,"text":"according to police reports .","depth":6},{"id":34,"text":"Mr. Scott ran away ,","depth":8},{"id":35,"text":"and Officer Slager chased him into a grassy lot","depth":9},{"id":36,"text":"that abuts a muffler shop .","depth":9},{"id":37,"text":"He fired his Taser , an electronic stun gun ,","depth":9},{"id":38,"text":"but it did not stop Mr. Scott ,","depth":9},{"id":39,"text":"according to police reports .","depth":8},{"id":40,"text":"Moments after the struggle , Officer Slager reported on his radio :","depth":7},{"id":41,"text":"\" Shots fired","depth":9},{"id":42,"text":"and the subject is down .","depth":10},{"id":43,"text":"He took my Taser , \"","depth":10},{"id":44,"text":"according to police reports .","depth":8},{"id":45,"text":"But the video ,","depth":7},{"id":46,"text":"which was taken by a bystander","depth":8},{"id":47,"text":"and provided to The New York Times by the Scott family ' s lawyer ,","depth":8},{"id":48,"text":"presents a different account .","depth":6},{"id":49,"text":"The video begins in the vacant lot ,","depth":7},{"id":50,"text":"apparently moments after Officer Slager fired his Taser .","depth":7},{"id":51,"text":"Wires ,","depth":10},{"id":52,"text":"which carry the electrical current from the stun gun ,","depth":10},{"id":53,"text":"appear to be extending from Mr. Scott ' s body","depth":9},{"id":54,"text":"as the two men tussle","depth":9},{"id":55,"text":"and Mr. Scott turns to run .","depth":9},{"id":56,"text":"Something","depth":11},{"id":57,"text":"- it is not clear","depth":12},{"id":58,"text":"whether it is the stun gun -","depth":12},{"id":59,"text":"is either tossed or knocked to the ground behind the two men ,","depth":10},{"id":60,"text":"and Officer Slager draws his gun ,","depth":10},{"id":61,"text":"the video shows .","depth":10},{"id":62,"text":"When the officer fires ,","depth":10},{"id":63,"text":"Mr. Scott appears to be 15 to 20 feet away","depth":11},{"id":64,"text":"and fleeing .","depth":11},{"id":65,"text":"He falls after the last of eight shots .","depth":9}],"relations":[{"parent":131,"left":0,"right":130,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":130,"left":82,"right":129,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":82,"left":75,"right":81,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":75,"left":74,"right":10,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":74,"left":69,"right":73,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":69,"left":1,"right":68,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":68,"left":2,"right":67,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":67,"left":3,"right":4,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":73,"left":71,"right":72,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":71,"left":5,"right":70,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":70,"left":6,"right":7,"relation":"causal","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":72,"left":8,"right":9,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":81,"left":11,"right":80,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":80,"left":77,"right":79,"relation":"topic","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":77,"left":12,"right":76,"relation":